### Notes - ingest (happy path)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "IBM weekly update",
  "author": "PM Desk",
  "text": "Trimmed IBM by ~20% after earnings; watch duration risk in credit sleeve.",
  "instrumentTickers": ["IBM"],
  "portfolioCodes": ["ALPHA"]
}

### Notes - ingest (multi-asset, multi-portfolio)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Weekly wrap",
  "author": "Risk",
  "text": "IBM down on guide; AAPL stable. Hedged with USTs.",
  "instrumentTickers": ["IBM", "AAPL", "US91282CJK11"],
  "portfolioCodes": ["ALPHA", "BETA"]
}

